By Sam Anokam  Nollywood director and producer, Chico Ejiro is one of the individuals that are yet to get over the shocking death of Frank Dallas. Ejiro is still mourning the passing away of the man, who is known to be his best friend. According to industry watchers, Ejiro and Dallas were like Siamese twins when he was alive.  They are hardly ever apart from each other, so much that they do business together, and travel together. Though Ejiro tries to conceal his pain, he has been keeping to himself in recent times. Those close to him noted that he is yet to recover from the shock of his best friendâ€™s death. 